Events
Flight Factory coordinates, runs, and sponsors over 20 events every year. Please see our current events below and reach out to support@flightfactorydiscs.com if you are interested in any bulk products or gift cards to support your next tournament.
2025 Downtown Disc Golf Experience Sponsored by Discraft
Welcome to the
Downtown Disc Golf Experience
at
Pensacola Blue Wahoos Stadium Sponsored by Discraft
! Get ready for a day filled with fun and excitement as you navigate through our unique disc golf course by the bay in downtown Pensacola. Whether you're a skilled player or a beginner looking to try something new, this event is perfect for all skill levels. Join us at the stadium for a day of friendly and outdoor fun. Don't miss out on this one-of-a-kind experience!
The event will feature the following fun and activities.
9 hole disc golf course throughout iconic Blue Wahoos stadium
Food, vendors, and fun games for all
VIP Event for VIP ticket holders
PDGA Flex Start tournament on Sunday
& More!

2025 Downtown Disc Golf Experience Sponsored by Discraft - Sunday Flex Start
This will be a PDGA C-Tier Flex Start event on Sunday 11/23. Participants will play 2 rounds of 9 holes consecutively. Please understand that there may be brief wait times once players complete their first 9 holes.
Player Pack(All Amateur Divisions):
-Unlimited round package and access to the course on Saturday and Sunday (11/22-11/23) - ($30 value)
-Limited Edition Custom Discraft Disc ($25 value)

About
FLIGHT FACTORY
So, what is Flight Factory all about? We specialize in custom, stock, and collectible Discs. We also offer a wide variety of apparel. You'll see unique pictures of nearly every disc that we sell.
We carry all of the major manufacturers, as well as many of the smaller ones as well. Whether you are a recreational player, touring pro, or a collector, we have the products to meet your needs. Customer service is our specialty. Prompt shipping, great communication, and superior products is how we will ensure that you always have a great experience with Flight Factory.
INTERNATIONAL ORDERS WELCOME
All international orders will be assigned a base shipping rate based on the order total, however, this may not be exact on larger orders. We will contact you prior to shipping if there is any need to update the shipping cost.
